---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 557
  - Title: The Imitation of Christ
    Location: III xlii
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Grace=Necessity
  - 199
---
If thou knewest perfectly to annihilate thyself, and to empty thyself
of all created love, then should I be constrained to flow into thee
with great abundance of grace.
